          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Per-Kind Admission Holds (kind_ceiling)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "description": "PENDING OTEL DEPLOYMENT (Phase B/D of the claude-subscription-usage-gate plan). Real Claude spend as reported by Claude Code's native OTel exporter (claude_code.cost.usage), once agent pods enable CLAUDE_CODE_ENABLE_TELEMETRY and the OTLP->Prometheus collector is wired via tatara-helmfile. Metric name shown (claude_code_cost_usage, dots->underscores) is the operator plan's named producer; confirm the exact scraped name (unit/type suffix the OTel Collector's Prometheus exporter adds) once the collector is live and correct this query if it differs.",
